            "id": "4578599",
            "title": "Oklo, Nvidia, Los Alamos National Laboratory to partner in supporting nuclear-powered AI factories",
            "description": "<html><body><p data-eci=\"true\">Oklo (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/OKLO\" title=\"Oklo Inc.\">OKLO</a></span>) up 7.9% pre-market Thursday after saying it agreed to <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/pr/20485019-oklo-nvidia-and-los-alamos-national-laboratory-collaborate-to-advance-nuclear-fuel-validation\" target=\"_self\" title=\"collaborate\">collaborate</a> with Nvidia (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/NVDA\" title=\"NVIDIA Corporation\">NVDA</a></span>) and <span>Los Alamos National Laboratory to advance critical nuclear infrastructure, AI-enabled research, and nuclear fuel R&amp;D at Los Alamos.</span></p>\n<p><span>By aligning Oklo’s (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/OKLO\" title=\"Oklo Inc.\">OKLO</a>) advanced sodium-fast-reactor platform, Nvidia's (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/NVDA\" title=\"NVIDIA Corporation\">NVDA</a>) AI infrastructure, and Los Alamos' world-leading expertise in materials science and nuclear fuels, the companies said they aim to lay the groundwork for a new class of mission-critical, high-assurance energy.</span></p>\n<p><span>Projects under the agreement include integrated full-stack solutions to support nuclear powered AI factories; AI development, including physics- and chemistry-trained AI models to support nuclear fuel R&amp;D; grid stabilization, reliability, and redundancy studies; materials science efforts focused on plutonium-bearing fuel; and proof-of-concept work related to the development of a nuclear-powered AI factory.</span></p>\n<p><span>\"We believe this will advance our plutonium-bearing fuel work on Oklo's Pluto reactor, which was selected under DoE's Reactor Pilot Program, and help bring resilient power in support of the Genesis Mission,\" Oklo (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/OKLO\" title=\"Oklo Inc.\">OKLO</a>) <span>CEO </span><span class=\"person\">Jacob DeWitte said.</span></span></p>\n<div class=\"signup_widget_placeholder\"></div>\n</body></html>",
            "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/assets/og_image_1200-29b2bfe1a595477db6826bd2126c63ac2091efb7ec76347a8e7f81ba17e3de6c.png",
